snippet.title: Dinner Party - Trailer
snippet.description:
Here is is! You have been invited! To the best dinner party of the decade!

In this new wacky game you will be convincing someone they are at a real dinner party. Using your wit and cunning, and some helpful puppets!

Dinner Party will be available on Itch.io on 11.07.17
